{
  "id": "5cdfcb0a9b024400178ef379",
  "title": "学習テクニックの有用性評価",
  "created": 1558170380,
  "updated": 1644743232,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5cdfcb0a9b024400178ef379",
      "text": "学習テクニックの有用性評価",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170380,
      "updated": 1558171037
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcb27aff09e00009acb4e",
      "text": "10種類の学習テクニックについて有用性を検証・比較した研究",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170407,
      "updated": 1644743232
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcb59aff09e00009acb52",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/844f1803af17ade1cf422c2a977f3b23]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170457,
      "updated": 1558170487
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcb77aff09e00009acb53",
      "text": "有用性が高いとされたPractice testingとDistributed practiceは[エンジニアの知的生産術]でも解説した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170487,
      "updated": 1644743125
    },
    {
      "id": "6208c9d5aff09e0000262f69",
      "text": "\tテストすること: [(3.4.1) テストは記憶の手段]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1644743125,
      "updated": 1644743163
    },
    {
      "id": "6208c9d9aff09e0000262f6a",
      "text": "\t学習の間隔を空けること: [(3.5.1) 忘れてから復習する]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1644743128,
      "updated": 1644743191
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcd0baff09e00009acb65",
      "text": " Practice testing: Self-testing or taking practice tests over to-be-learned material",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170892,
      "updated": 1558170903
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcd0caff09e00009acb67",
      "text": " Distributed practice: Implementing a schedule of practice that spreads out study activities over time",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170892,
      "updated": 1558170905
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcd0baff09e00009acb66",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170892,
      "updated": 1558170892
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcc02aff09e00009acb61",
      "text": "有用性が中くらいとされたもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170626,
      "updated": 1558170852
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcce3aff09e00009acb64",
      "text": "\tElaborative interrogation: Generating an explanation for why an explicitly stated fact or concept is true",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170852,
      "updated": 1558170863
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcd2aaff09e00009acb69",
      "text": "\t\tなぜ正しいのかを説明する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170922,
      "updated": 1558170958
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcc02aff09e00009acb62",
      "text": "\tSelf-explanation: Explaining how new information is related to known information, or explaining steps taken during problem solving",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170626,
      "updated": 1558170932
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcd50aff09e00009acb6b",
      "text": "\t\t他の情報との関連や、導出過程を解説する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170961,
      "updated": 1558170979
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcdfaaff09e00009acb6d",
      "text": "\t\t[Scrapbox]で解説を書くことは、他の情報との関連を解説することになりそうだ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558171131,
      "updated": 1558171155
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcbb0aff09e00009acb57",
      "text": "\tInterleaved practice Implementing a schedule of practice that mixes different kinds of problems, or a schedule of study that mixes different kinds of material, within a single study session",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170545,
      "updated": 1558170929
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcd31aff09e00009acb6a",
      "text": "\t\t異なる種類の学習対象を混ぜる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1558170929,
      "updated": 1558171004
    },
    {
      "id": "5cdfcd6baff09e00009acb6c",
